text: Sofia Middleton (born 12 March 1993) is a Chilean competitive sailor. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the women's 470 class. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean female sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Chile Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – 470
